title: Thanks
author: rydenstrife
pages:
#- Dear Avalo,§0
§0
§0I tried to see what you don't have much of because I wanted to do what I could to get it for you. You always helped me out from the beginning. It's almost been two years. In and out but it feels like forever and when you were here, you 
#- were always ready to lend a hand. You've spared me time and diamonds while offering your own to help me out. You kept me company while I hid from LADS and when I just wanted a friend to hang out with. I wish there was more I could give you to repay, and I
#- gotta say, name tags are incredibly fucking difficult to get my hands on apparently. Redstone isnt in the highest supply and I have like 3 slimeballs. I know you're not the materialistic type of person, but I really just wanted to say thank you for every-
#- thing and give back what I can of something that you need for once. Anyway, thanks again for everything you've done. It's an honor to know you and I wish you didn't live so far away. I'm sure we'd make really good friends here in the real world. So yeah. 
#- If theres ever any other way I can repay you for our history of you being amazing, let me know. I'll always do what I can.  :)

Drew
#- 